{
  "texts": [
    "This is the reason why we selected texts according to their similar length or semantic content (by applying the KL distance on the semantic annotations) and the lexical similarity (Dai et al. 's method [49]).",
    "For our task, these methods are complementary and are more adequate than other alternatives such as selecting texts according to the authors' demographics or the publication channel (e.g.",
